<br>
Vendor windows are now placable on the screen and it remembers it.  <br>
<br>
Holding down the Right mouse button over an icon still works as it does now, the info window goes away when you release.  If you left click while the info window is open it will stay up. <br>
<br>
Friends list is in it's own box now.<br>
<br>
I haven't checked out the tracking skill yet.<br>
<br>
If you want to change video resolution, you no longer have to cycle through every other resolution until you get to the one you want.  It works like Windows does now.  Select the resolution, the color dept (16 or 32 bits), hit apply.  It changes to the desired settings.  It asks if the settings are correct.  Click yes and they stay.  Hit no, or wait 15 second (incase you can't read the screen) it reverts back.<br>
<br>
Nice Job Verant.  Can't wait for it to go Live.  Can't wait for the Bazaar either! =D<br>
<br>
